Hi Swati,

Suppose your meter stick is marked so that you can measure the
distance to the nearest centimeter.  You might be off by as much as
half a centimeter, so the percentage error would be 

  1/2 cm     ?
 -------- = ---
   20 cm    100

Does that make sense?

